        {
          "text": "Odette full name is Princess Odette Alvin."
        },
        {
          "text": "The sword Odette carries is used as a focus for her spells. She doesn't use the sword by conventional means."
        },
        {
          "text": "Since the founding of the empire by Gaius, the ruling Monian dynasty has never changed, as Silvanna is a direct descendant of Gaius. This means that Odette and Silvanna and Dyrroth have a common ancestor."
        },
        {
          "text": "The fact that the ruling dynasty has never changed shows us its connection to Vexana, who was also a princess of the Monian Empire."
        },
        {
          "text": "It is hinted in one of her quotes that the sword is a gift. The sword gifted by Lancelot."
        },
        {
          "text": "Lancelot is referenced in two of her quotes: \"Don't ask me why a mage is carrying a sword!\" \"This sword is a gift.\""
        },
        {
          "text": "Odette is inspired by a character with the same name in Swan Lake.",
          "links": [
            {
              "text": "Swan Lake",
              "type": "external",
              "site": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Swan_Lake"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Her \"Black Swan\" skin is also a reference to another character from the same opera."
        },
        {
          "text": "The music from her Ultimate, Swan Song is from Tchaikovsky's Swan Lake (Ballet Suitte), OP. 20"
        },
        {
          "text": "She was purchasable with at first. Now, she can only be obtained by new players through quests, be bought in the Fragment Shop using  Hero Fragments, or in the Lucky Shop using  Lucky Gems.",
          "links": [
            {
